posting_body: ['The Durham features just the right blend of charm and the ideal location for your next home.', 'Our community offers a variety of spacious apartment homes ranging from one-bedroom to three-bedroom floor plans.', 'Residents enjoy breathtaking views from our balconies, generous closet space, quartz counters, plank flooring and much, much more!', 'The Durham is nestled in the suburb of Edina with easy access to several major highways.', '-Dedicated Laundry Facilities with High Efficiency Equipment and Onsite Dry Cleaning', '-Quality-crafted cabinetry with under cabinet lighting', '-Spacious, walk-in closets in select apartment homes', '-Host Out of Town Guests Overnight in the Guest Suite', '-24-Hour Fitness Center Furnished with Life Fitness Equipment', '-Resident Portal: Enter Maintenance Requests Online when Convenient', '-Whirlpool stainless steel appliance suite with French door refrigerator and backless range', '-High Intensity UVC Lamp Coupled with Bionic iWave Air Purifying Systems', '-Stay Connected!', 'Wi-Fi in all Amenity Spaces', '-Engineered wood plank flooring throughout', '-The Event Features a Demonstration Kitchen with Enough Room to Entertain a Few Close Friends or a Crowd', '-The Board Room is Perfect for Private Meetings', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
